# Data import (scoped)

- One canonical taxonomy (`core/place_taxonomy.py`); map external categories explicitly.
- Imports idempotent/restart-safe; no duplicates by slug alone (city scope, coords, source id).
- Imported places need explicit publication/visibility flags — no title-based hiding.
- Preserve source, confidence, freshness; shadow writes safe on re-run.

Before taxonomy/import changes: check import scripts, route filters, admin filters, tests.
